articles.title: Yellen says government will help SVB depositors but rules out bailout - Financial Times
articles.description: Treasury secretary says policies are being formulated to stem fallout of tech lender’s collapse
articles.content:
Janet Yellen said on Sunday that the US government was working closely with banking regulators to help depositors at Silicon Valley Bank, but dismissed the idea of a bailout.
